## Миграции PostgreSQL (домен)

```sql
-- 001_init: users, organizations (type), org_members (role), api_keys, sessions
-- 002_billing: plans (per org_type), subscriptions (org_id), payments, ticket_quotas
-- 003_installations: installations (client_org_id, criticality, snapshot_allowed, emergency_contact),
--                    installation_products (product_id, version, environment JSONB),
--                    products (manufacturer_org_id, slug, kind IN plc/scada/hmi/drive/sensor/network/other)
-- 004_entitlements: entitlements (installation_product_id, serial_or_license, supplier_org_id,
--                    integrator_org_id, purchase_date, warranty_until, verified_by IN manufacturer/partner/client_claim)
-- 005_docs: doc_sources (product_id, version, s3_original_key, content_hash, status, page_count),
--           doc_chunks (doc_source_id, page_number, s3_page_key, content_md, embedding vector(3072), section)
-- 006_tickets: tickets (installation_id, type IN typical/defect/warranty/application/cross_vendor,
--              priority IN emergency/degraded/question, status, ball_owner_org_id nullable),
--              ticket_events (append-only: kind, actor_org_id, payload JSONB, created_at),
--              ticket_attachments (s3_key), ticket_links (стыковые: parent/related)
-- 007_sla: support_zones (manufacturer_org_id, policy JSONB: версии/границы/часы — YAML-импорт),
--          sla_policies (plan_id, priority, react_minutes), sla_timers (ticket_id, deadline, state)
-- 008_kb: kb_articles (product_id nullable, version_range, origin_ticket_id nullable, status, slug, content_md),
--         kb_embeddings
-- 009_agent: agent_conversations, agent_messages (citations JSONB), qualification_feedback,
--            golden_sets, golden_questions (question, reference_answer, must_cite_page)
-- 010_ops: usage_log, audit_log, fallback_log (needed_role, missing_org_name, ticket_id), notifications
```

Ключевые констрейнты:
- tickets.status конечный автомат; переходы ТОЛЬКО через ticket_events (триггер или сервис-слой).
- entitlements: UNIQUE(installation_product_id, serial_or_license).
- doc_chunks.page_number NOT NULL — цитата без страницы невалидна.
- support_zones.policy валидируется схемой при импорте; невалидная политика не применяется.

